name: GunZoo.com
overview:
Gunzoo is an online information repository for all things firearms. We feel there is a large void in the online firearms space and seek to fill that void with compelling firearms content. Our first release includes a firearms comparison engine providing firearms enthusiasts with a powerful tool that enables them to research all the options in the marketplace before making a buying decision. This compare tool offers a stat-by-stat comparison of thousands of firearms. Also, in our first release, we are introducing a news feed that will deliver the latest Firearms Industry news. We hope you find these news articles informative and pertinent to your interests.

In the coming months and years we have several surprises that we are extremely excited to bring to you so, stand-by, it only gets better from here!
